":"{}</p>"},"sn14.17:5.1":{"pli":"Dhātusova, bhikkhave, sattā saṃsandanti samenti. ","eng":"Sentient beings join together and converge because of an element: ","html":"<p>{}"},"sn14.17:5.2":{"pli":"Saddhā saddhehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti; ","eng":"the faithful with the faithful, ","html":"{}"},"sn14.17:5.3":{"pli":"hirimanā hirimanehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti; ","eng":"the conscientious with the conscientious, ","html":"{}"},"sn14.17:5.4":{"pli":"ottappino ottappīhi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti; ","eng":"the prudent with the prudent, ","html":"{}"},"sn14.17:5.5":{"pli":"bahussutā bahussutehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti; ","eng":"the learned with the learned, ","html":"{}"},"sn14.17:5.6":{"pli":"āraddhavīriyā āraddhavīriyehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti; ","eng":"the energetic with the energetic, ","html":"{}"},"sn14.17:5.7":{"pli":"upaṭṭhitassatino upaṭṭhitassatīhi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti; ","eng":"the mindful with the mindful, ","html":"{}"},"sn14.17:5.8":{"pli":"paññavanto paññavantehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samenti. ","eng":"and the wise with the wise. ","html":"{}"},"sn14.17:5.9":{"pli":"Atītampi kho, bhikkhave, addhānaṃ …pe… ","eng":"In the past … ","html":"{}"},"sn14.17:5.10":{"pli":"anāgatampi kho, bhikkhave …pe… ","eng":"In the future … ","html":"{}"},"sn14.17:5.11":{"pli":"etarahipi kho, bhikkhave, paccuppannaṃ addhānaṃ dhātusova sattā saṃsandanti samenti. ","eng":"At present, too, sentient beings join together and converge because of an element. …” ","html":"{}"},"sn14.17:5.12":{"pli":"Saddhā saddhehi saddhiṃ …pe… ","html":"{}"},"sn14.17:5.13":{"pli":"paññavanto paññavantehi saddhiṃ saṃsandanti samentī”ti. ","html":"{}</p>"},"sn14.17:5.14":{"pli":"Sattamaṃ. ","html":"<p class='endsutta'>{}</p></article>"}},"sn14.18":{"sn14.18:0.1":{"pli":"Saṃyutta Nikāya 14.18 ","eng":"Linked Discourses 14.18 ","html":"<article id='sn14.18'><header><ul><li class='division'>{}</li>"},"sn14.18:0.2":{"pli":"2. Dutiyavagga ","eng":"Chapter Two ","html":"<li>{}</li></ul>"